    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Layering Beats \r\n\r\nYour friend Caroline really likes the beats in Chantaje by Shakira, but she wants to add little sound effects to the ends of the tracks to create small moments at the end of the beat. She's already picked out her Beat and Effect samples and now she just needs to arrange them:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/006d907c692bb18b5e6e9be299b14b10-image-1744151092143.png)\r\n\r\nYou can choose which beats and effects to use, but the effect should come in at the last moment before the beat ends.\r\n\r\nTo pass this level, your timeline must look similar to the image where the effect track happens just as the beat is about to end, and then a new beat starts. Your code should have 3 different beats and effects!\r\n\r\n",
